snippet.title: EverQuest 2: Kunark Ascending [Official Trailer]
snippet.description:
Kunark Ascending is available NOW at https://bit.ly/EQ2-KA

Kunark Ascending is the 13th EverQuest II expansion, featuring exciting new adventures, dungeons, quests, and gear.

It will take great courage to stand against the coming darkness. When the Tenets of Hate ascend, will you stand against them? Norrath remains in danger from Lanys T’Vyl and her ruthless pursuit of power. Journey to Obulus Frontier in North Kunark and adventure through areas both familiar and undiscovered as you attempt to protect the last Chaos Stone from Lanys’ evil clutches!

Did you know you can play EverQuest II for FREE? https://www.everquest2.com/register

Like us on Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/EverQuest2 
Follow us on Twitter: https://twitter.com/everquestii 
Join the discussion on the official forums: http://ow.ly/QtJn309uZ6z
